msgid "EIC"
msgstr "EIC"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/eic.rst:4
msgid ""
"EIC(Elastic Instant Cache) is a distributed database designed for LLM KV "
"Cache. It supports RDMA, GDR and has the capabilities of distributed "
"disaster tolerance and expansion. You can understand the principles and "
"architecture of EIC through these articles:"
msgstr "EIC（弹性瞬时缓存）是为 LLM KV Cache 设计的分布式数据库。它支持 RDMA、GDR，并具备分布式灾难容忍和扩展能力。您可以通过这些文章了解 EIC 的原理和架构："

